Headache(Headache)
MusclePains(MusclePains)
FeelingTired(FeelingTired)

# Conditions for feeling tired
Person(x) ∧ Glu(y) → FeelTiredWhen(x, y)

# Properties of a 'Glu' condition
Glu(x) → Fever(x)
Glu(x) → Headache(x)
Glu(x) → MusclePains(x)
Glu(x) → FeelingTired(x)

# Relationship between virus occurrence and disease occurrence
OccurIn(mp_virus, x) → OccurIn(mp, x)

# Occurrence of Monkeypox in humans and animals (derived from virus occurrence and the rule above, but explicitly stated for clarity)
Monkeypox(x) → OccurIn(x, humans)
Monkeypox(x) → OccurIn(x, animals)

# Conclusion:
¬SymptomOf(Coughing, mp)
